name: iphone 5/5s skin - "Pastel Seduction"
description:
These skins are removable covers for protecting and customizing your phone. They come with high quality graphics. The best part is that the application of them is easy (so no worries about getting it right the first time), and if you ever get tired of your awesome cover you can take it off with no residue. Your phone will look as new as it did before you put it on!

The front of the phone comes with a screensaver as well, that continues the image of the phone skin. The screen saver will be send to you via email with your order.
